# Financial OS

- Manual-first personal finance platform — see `AGENTS.md` for full guidance
- Monorepo: `frontend/` (Next.js) + `backend/` (FastAPI)
- All backend routes use the `/api` prefix
- Business logic in `services/`, database access in `repositories/`
- Run Python commands with `uv` from `backend/`
- Keep imports at the top of files; no inline imports
- Use shadcn/ui + Tailwind; support dark mode
- Credit card payments are transfers, not expenses
